Domator.text: Invalid is now quite well and will write you

Domitrix.text: Invalid recommended change of air by doctor, and as soon as convalescent will go to ---

Domo.text: Invalid the same, doctor recommends change of air

Donarium.text: Is able to undertake the journey

Donax.text: Is unable to undertake the journey

Drapeta.text: Can take no nourishment, come if possible

Dryades.text: Operation has been performed without success

Duellum.text: Is able to be removed from bed

Dulcedo.text: Is unable to be removed from bed

Dulcifera.text: Is able to be removed to another room

Dummodo.text: Is unable to be removed to another room

Duodecim.text: Passed a sleepless night, and is feverish this morning

Duplex.text: Slept well, and has taken nourishment this morning

Fabrica.text: Taken ill, cannot come this week

Fabulose.text: Taken ill slightly, do not be alarmed

Facesso.text: Taken ill slightly, letter by post

Facetus.text: Taken ill slightly, no necessity for doctor
